import { Component, Input } from '@angular/core'; import { CarsService } from "../app/shared/services/cars.service"; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { listaCarros: any[]; listaMotos: any[]; filtroCarro: string; filtroMoto: string; constructor(protected carsService: CarsService ) { } generateCarros(){ this.listaCarros = this.carsService.generateCarros(); } generateMotos(){ this.listaMotos = this.carsService.generateMotos(); } limparTudo(){ this.listaCarros = []; this.listaMotos = []; } aplcarFiltroCarro(event){ const value = event.target.value.toUpperCase(); this.listaCarros = this.carsService.generateCarros() .filter(carro => carro.marca.toUpperCase().includes(value)) } aplcarFiltroMoto(event){ const value = event.target.value.toUpperCase(); this.listaMotos = this.carsService.generateMotos() .filter(moto => moto.marca.toUpperCase().includes(value)) } }
